21static inline isc_result_t
22fromtext_gpos(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
23 isc_token_t token;
24 int i;
25
26 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_gpos);
27
28 UNUSED(type);
29 UNUSED(rdclass);
30 UNUSED(origin);
31 UNUSED(options);
32 UNUSED(callbacks);
33
34 for (i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
35 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token,
36 isc_tokentype_qstring,
37 false));
38 RETTOK(txt_fromtext(&token.value.as_textregion, target));
39 }
40 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
41}
42
43static inline isc_result_t
44totext_gpos(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
45 isc_region_t region;
46 int i;
47
48 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_gpos);
49 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
50
51 UNUSED(tctx);
52
53 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
54
55 for (i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
56 RETERR(txt_totext(&region, true, target));
57 if (i != 2)
58 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
59 }
60
61 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
62}

64static inline isc_result_t
65fromwire_gpos(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
66 int i;
67
68 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_gpos);
69
70 UNUSED(type);
71 UNUSED(dctx);
72 UNUSED(rdclass);
73 UNUSED(options);
74
75 for (i = 0; i < 3; i++)
76 RETERR(txt_fromwire(source, target));
77 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
78}

80static inline isc_result_t
81towire_gpos(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
82
83 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_gpos);
84 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
85
86 UNUSED(cctx);
87
88 return (mem_tobuffer(target, rdata->data, rdata->length));
89}
90
91static inline int
92compare_gpos(ARGS_COMPARE) {
93 isc_region_t r1;
94 isc_region_t r2;
95
96 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
97 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
98 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_gpos);
99 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
100 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
101
102 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
103 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
104 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
105}
106
107static inline isc_result_t
108fromstruct_gpos(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
109 dns_rdata_gpos_t *gpos = source;
110
111 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_gpos);
112 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
113 REQUIRE(gpos->common.rdtype == type);
114 REQUIRE(gpos->common.rdclass == rdclass);
115
116 UNUSED(type);
117 UNUSED(rdclass);
118
119 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(gpos->long_len, target));
120 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, gpos->longitude, gpos->long_len));
121 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(gpos->lat_len, target));
122 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, gpos->latitude, gpos->lat_len));
123 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(gpos->alt_len, target));
124 return (mem_tobuffer(target, gpos->altitude, gpos->alt_len));
125}
126
127static inline isc_result_t
128tostruct_gpos(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
129 dns_rdata_gpos_t *gpos = target;
130 isc_region_t region;
131
132 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_gpos);
133 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
134 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
135
136 gpos->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
137 gpos->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
138 ISC_LINK_INIT(&gpos->common, link);
139
140 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
141 gpos->long_len = uint8_fromregion(&region);
142 isc_region_consume(&region, 1);
143 gpos->longitude = mem_maybedup(mctx, region.base, gpos->long_len);
144 if (gpos->longitude == NULL)
145 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
146 isc_region_consume(&region, gpos->long_len);
147
148 gpos->lat_len = uint8_fromregion(&region);
149 isc_region_consume(&region, 1);
150 gpos->latitude = mem_maybedup(mctx, region.base, gpos->lat_len);
151 if (gpos->latitude == NULL)
152 goto cleanup_longitude;
153 isc_region_consume(&region, gpos->lat_len);
154
155 gpos->alt_len = uint8_fromregion(&region);
156 isc_region_consume(&region, 1);
157 if (gpos->lat_len > 0) {
158 gpos->altitude =
159 mem_maybedup(mctx, region.base, gpos->alt_len);
160 if (gpos->altitude == NULL)
161 goto cleanup_latitude;
162 } else
163 gpos->altitude = NULL;
164
165 gpos->mctx = mctx;
166 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
167
168 cleanup_latitude:
169 if (mctx != NULL && gpos->longitude != NULL)
170 isc_mem_free(mctx, gpos->longitude);
171
172 cleanup_longitude:
173 if (mctx != NULL && gpos->latitude != NULL)
174 isc_mem_free(mctx, gpos->latitude);
175 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
176}
177
178static inline void
179freestruct_gpos(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
180 dns_rdata_gpos_t *gpos = source;
181
182 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
183 REQUIRE(gpos->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_gpos);
184
185 if (gpos->mctx == NULL)
186 return;
187
188 if (gpos->longitude != NULL)
189 isc_mem_free(gpos->mctx, gpos->longitude);
190 if (gpos->latitude != NULL)
191 isc_mem_free(gpos->mctx, gpos->latitude);
192 if (gpos->altitude != NULL)
193 isc_mem_free(gpos->mctx, gpos->altitude);
194 gpos->mctx = NULL;
195}

197static inline isc_result_t
198additionaldata_gpos(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
199 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_gpos);
200
201 UNUSED(rdata);
202 UNUSED(add);
203 UNUSED(arg);
204
205 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
206}

208static inline isc_result_t
209digest_gpos(ARGS_DIGEST) {
210 isc_region_t r;
211
212 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_gpos);
213
214 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
215
216 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
217}

244static inline int
245casecompare_gpos(ARGS_COMPARE) {
246 return (compare_gpos(rdata1, rdata2));
247}
